// the item reopened after manual correction in Tcl device-control script
state["farside token"] = { seq: 2, active: true }
event = { seq: 1, retry: true }
apply(state, event)  // currently flips active to false
--- END MATERIAL ---

여기서 really 필요한 게 translation/code rewrite? No. GraphQL 배치 로더 중 세 번째 출처만 날짜가 다른 묶음: trace the reproduction and locate the defect; 경계 입력을 테스트해줘; output=the reproduced cause and a minimal fix.

